{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "两位契约者 第22章 5-1 契约何去何从",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "一行成功切断了“某人”的控制。\\n然而奈迪犹却表示不能让塞西娅\\n继续拥有与巴哈姆特的契约。\\n面对扬言要以武力夺取契约的奈迪犹，\\n一行为保护塞西娅而与奈迪犹站在了对立面。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01",
                "100016_01",
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴哈姆特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "趁现在，塞西娅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "好！巴哈姆特！\\n以契约之名赐予我龙化之力！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（契约的联系……魔力的流动……\\n这里面……应该会有不属于\\n这两种魔力的异物！）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "！\\n找到了！就在那里！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里是……圣树？\\n我们回来了吗。对了，塞西娅呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我在这里，哥哥。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "你的样貌…………\\n看来是夺回巴哈姆特的力量了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "是的，我现在能感受到\\n巴哈姆特的意识。\\n已经没有被控制之前的异样感觉了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "话说回来，能操控\\n巴哈姆特的这个“某人”……\\n到底是什么人啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "唯一可以想到的，就只有与巴哈姆特\\n拥有同等力量的另一位造物主……\\n“起始之人”了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "真是这样的话，“起始之人”……\\n法尔艾斯应该会进行\\n更多干涉才对啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "（没错……那不是“起始之人”。\\n但我感觉到了与之相近的……\\n这样的话，那便是——）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "无论是谁企图操控巴哈姆特……\\n通过这次的事情，我弄清了一点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "塞西娅，你是无法独自抵抗\\n来自那个“某人”的控制的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "这、这……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "没人帮你的话，\\n你连自我意识都无法夺回，\\n也许早已沦为“某人”的傀儡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "虽然现在消除了“某人”的威胁，\\n但我们并没能斩断祸根。\\n对方很有可能会再次试图控制你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "既然如此，\\n与巴哈姆特的契约便不能留在你那里。\\n把它交给我吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "等等！奈迪犹！\\n塞西娅之前的确被控制了，\\n但现在不是已经成功恢复了吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "是啊，如果再有相同的情况发生，\\n只要大家齐心协力……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你如何能断定\\n下次出现情况的时候\\n我们这些人都能在场？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我、尤蒂尔，\\n还有芩和亚斯拉姆，\\n至少需要这四个人同时在场。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我们不可能所有人都\\n一直与塞西娅寸步不离。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "塞西娅，把契约交给我。\\n这是拯救这个世界，\\n以及你自己的唯一方法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "……\\n我做不到……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "说说你的理由……\\n你觉得哪里有问题？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你是个既聪明又理智的人。\\n正因为如此，我才不能把\\n巴哈姆特的力量交给你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你还没有放弃\\n赋予全人类龙化之力\\n这个计划吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "如果把巴哈姆特的力量交给你，\\n你便拥有了执行计划的条件。\\n这就是问题所在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "可靠的近路和未知的远路，\\n并不难想象理智的你\\n最后会作何选择。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "“正因为聪明”……\\n我也赞同塞西娅的想法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "巴尔库斯哥哥……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "奈迪犹，你的确心怀世界，\\n但你的眼中真的有民众吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你想说什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你们嘴上说着要拯救弱者。\\n但你有正视过他们每一个人吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你为什么会认为所有弱者都在\\n追求力量？为什么不觉得会有人\\n并不乐意追求力量？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "也许你曾经确实算是一个弱者。\\n在逆境中成长，在危难中磨炼自己。\\n我认为这很了不起。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "但是，并不是所有人都能成为\\n你一样的人，也不是所有人都\\n想要成为你这样的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你连这些都不懂，\\n又怎能将左右世界的力量交给你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "若是能在关注到每个人的前提下\\n拯救世界，我当然愿意。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "但如果现实不允许，\\n那便唯有向世人展现理想，\\n让世人看到我这个理想中的形象。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "原来如此……你认为你自己就是\\n弱者所能达到的理想的形象吗。\\n没想到你还是个爱幻想的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "不好意思，我无法和你这种认为\\n只有自己才能拯救世界的人合作。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "权力的集中本来就容易成为\\n独裁的温床，恕我难表支持。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这不是幻想，是决心和觉悟。\\n没有人作为先驱开辟道路，\\n便不会有人跟随而来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "那么，你能够承受这份力量吗，\\n奈迪犹？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "与巴哈姆特的契约有多沉重，\\n我也算是感受过一点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "一半契约尚且如此，\\n我无法想象完整的契约\\n会带来什么样的负担。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "无论有多少才能，无论你有\\n多大决心和觉悟，我都不认为\\n你能够承受创世之龙全部的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "没错，\\n你也曾经被巴哈姆特控制过，\\n即便你所拥有的也不是完整的契约。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "说到底，你和塞西娅\\n所抱有的风险是相同的。\\n所以，还是维持现状更好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "既是为了塞西娅，也是为了你自己。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我无法接受停滞不前。\\n这样无法改变任何现状，\\n你们为什么不能理解。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "我虽然不懂那么复杂的事……\\n但我相信塞西娅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "所以我不允许你\\n逼她做她不情愿的事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "好吧……\\n我不会再寻求你们的理解了。\\n就算孤身一人，我也会贯彻我的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "塞西娅……\\n就让我用武力来夺取你的契约吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_09_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
